For initializing a Repository use --> "git init"

For adding files to staging area:
    01_ "git add file.ext" --> adding one file
    02_ "git add file.ext file2.ext" --> adding multiple files
    03_ "git add *.ext" --> adding all files with this extension
    04_ "git add ."  --> adding all files

For Viewing the status:
    01_ "git status --> view full status
    02_ "git status -"s" --> view short status

For Committing the staging files:
    01_ "git commit -m 'Your message.'" --> one line message
    02_ "git commit" --> open editor to type a long message

For Skipping the staging area use --> "git commit -am 'Your message.'"

For Removing files:
    01_ "git rm file.ext" --> removes from working dir and staging area
    02_ "git rm --cached file.ext" --> removes from staging area only

For Renaming or Moving files use --> "git mv file.ext file2.ext"
